  "description": "A sweeping panoramic view of a city nestled along a bay, dominated by dramatic, layered cloud formations. The cityscape is visible in the distance, appearing somewhat hazy and compact beneath a sprawling network of grey and white clouds. A bridge stretches across the water, connecting parts of the urban area. Lush green trees and vegetation occupy the foreground, partially obscuring the view and adding depth to the composition. The overall lighting is soft and diffused, with a warm glow peeking through gaps in the clouds, hinting at a potential sunrise or sunset. The bay appears calm, reflecting the muted tones of the sky. The scene evokes a sense of expansive scale and natural beauty.",
